Barroso Sees Chance of Faster Payout of EU Subsidies to Greece

-- B y   J a m e s   G .   N e u g e r
-- 
2011-10-13T07:41:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/barroso-sees-chance-of-faster-payout-of-eu-subsidies-to-greece.html
Greece  could gain faster access to
15 billion euros in European infrastructure subsidies under
proposals to “frontload” the aid, European Commission
President  Jose Barroso  said.  “The problem is not lack of money, the problem is lack of
administrative capacity,” Barroso said at a Friends of Europe
conference in Brussels today. “We have to mobilize all
instruments to leverage growth.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James G. Neuger at 
 jneuger@bloomberg.net  